# Alembic Project Skills

Project Skills are AI knowledge documents in `Alembic/skills/`, tracked in Git.

## Discovery & Loading

- **List**: `alembic_skill({ operation: "list" })` — all available Skills (builtin + project)
- **Load**: `alembic_skill({ operation: "load", name: "<skill>" })` — full Skill content
- **Create**: `alembic_skill({ operation: "create", name, description, content })` — new project Skill

## Built-in Skills (5)

| Skill | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| `alembic-create` | Submit knowledge candidates (V3 fields, validation) |
| `alembic-recipes` | Project standard context (Recipe search, retrieval) |
| `alembic-guard` | Code compliance checking against Recipes |
| `alembic-structure` | Project structure discovery & knowledge graph |
| `alembic-devdocs` | Save development documents (ADRs, debug reports) |

## Priority

- **Project Skills > Built-in Skills** — same name → project overrides builtin
- **Skills = read-only reference** — load via MCP tool, do not edit SKILL.md directly
